  "title": "Looking for 6 Months Locum Pharmacy Technician #HGAT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Process prescriptions and dispense medications to polyclinic patients</li><li>Support Medication Delivery Service (MDS) and PILBOX service for remote collection of medications</li><li>Provide Tele-dispensing services (where applicable)</li><li>Assist in video consultation (VC) and medication reconciliation</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Pharmaceutical Science or Certificate in Pharmacy Technician Course (under MOH, PSS or its equivalent) required</li><li>Previous experience as a pharmacy technician experience preferred</li><li>Minimum commitment: 6 months</li><li>Looking for candidates who are comfortable with travelling as candidates may be posted in different locations</li></ul><p>Interested candidates can write in to Ann at <a href=\"mailto:pharma@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">pharma@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p><p><br />\n<strong>Ann Goh Xin Ting</strong><br /><strong>\nR1875289</strong></p><p><strong>Recruit\nExpress Pte Ltd</strong><br /><strong>\nE.A License: 99C4599</strong></p>",
